  <div class="card-six-info six-text col-10" style="margin:0 auto 50px auto;">
  <h2 style="color:#AC7FDD; padding:8px">What is Six Degrees of Seperation?</h2>
        <p>Musicians like to mingle. They collaborate, change bands, cover each others songs and share producers.
        Six degrees of seperation explores these links by suggesting six albums all linked to each other by real world events. Starting from your chosen album,
        the next suggested album could be linked by a guitarist that played in both bands or a producer that worked on both albums or an act that performed with another onstage. The list is endless.
        This provides a rich variety of suggested material that could span different artists, genres or points in time but are linked by real world events that actually happened.
        </p>
  </div>


